title: Gravity (Marvel)
description:
Greg Willis was born and grew up in Sheboygan, Wisconsin. During the summer after his high school graduation, an as-of-yet unexplained accident granted him the ability to manipulate gravity. Greg enrolls at New York University, intending to succeeding both academically and as a superhero. But he finds that university and being a fledgling superhero in the big city isn't all that easy.



Released on http://ComicPirates.info
